name: Ipanema's Ethset
description: This is a photo from Ipanema's Rio de Janeiro, where everyday people go to appreciate and sometimes even give a round of applause for the sun's rise and set, as Crypto rise and set we stay, like in Ipanema mere observers.  This is a collaboration between 3 artists photography from @2t_fotografia, music from @illu.illuu, and photo bash and animation from @cavalcanti_felipe
